node.text: We all know that Angelina’s wedding speech was a train wreck and caused havoc on our family ... so when I was asked to do the speech at Angelina’s redo wedding , instead of writing a better speech, I wanted to perform a speech that was worse. The bridesmaids set the bar so low.. so why not go lower? why not only get bood, but also get things thrown at me ?! We’ve been roasting Angelina for 10 years , so why not do a REVERSE roast of her ? I am always happy to be made fun of and bood by my roommates.. as long as we are all laughing together, and not crying. The end .

node.text: Bruh, a few months ago I didn’t know what a Paso Doble even was, but here I am giving it my best shot to this routine choreographed by my boy @kikinyemchek with my dance partner @ashleycmeverett for my last performance... Sorry for all the sappy posts but I really can’t express how much I enjoyed this process of learning how to dance and being the hammer head... BTW this secret get up is how we moved around the set at all times and recorded videos so no one would know it was me . Enjoy @maskeddancerfox #TheMaskedDancer

node.text: A few years ago I filmed a magical show with my mom. Let’s face it, you guys love her more than me, and always say that we should have our own food show. Well, we did! It was called Vinny and Ma Eat America where I took my mom on a cross country road trip to try new things, and it was as hilarious as you can imagine. Unfortunately, those were my “off years “ when Jersey Shore wasn’t on anymore, so it probably didn’t get the ratings it deserved. I’ve gained a lot more of a spotlight since then , and I  truly think if more people saw it , her and I would still be doing it today. The reason why I’m bringing it up now is because I always wanted to share the show with the 2021 audience that I have now, but never had a way to do it. But I just discovered you can get the show on @discoveryplus . This is not an ad. I just truly think it was a special product and want as many people to enjoy Mamma Paola as possible . So check it out !
